<i>noun</i>: 애걸 [애걸], 사정 [사ː정], 문전걸식 [문전걸씩], 동냥 [동ː냥], 구걸 [구걸], 걸식 [걸씩] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>애걸 [애걸]</dt><br>
<dd>begging; pleading</dd><br>
<dd>바라는 것을 들어 달라고 간절하게 빎.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of asking earnestly for something that one wishes for.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>사정 [사ː정]</dt><br>
<dd>1. situation; circumstances</dd><br>
<dd>일의 형편이나 이유.</dd><br>
<dd>The situation or reason for an incident.</dd><br>
<dd>2. pleading; begging</dd><br>
<dd>다른 사람에게 일의 형편을 말하고 도와줄 것을 부탁함.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of explaining the situation of something to someone and asking for his/her help.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>문전걸식 [문전걸씩]</dt><br>
<dd>begging</dd><br>
<dd>이 집 저 집 돌아다니며 식량을 구걸해 얻어먹음.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of going door-to-door to beg for food.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>동냥 [동ː냥]</dt><br>
<dd>1. begging; begged stuff</dd><br>
<dd>거지나 가난한 사람이 음식이나 돈 등을 달라고 비는 일. 또는 그렇게 하여 얻은 것.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of a beggar or poor person asking for food, money, etc., or something obtained by doing so.</dd><br>
<dd>2. offering</dd><br>
<dd>승려가 사람들에게 시주를 받으러 다니는 일. 또는 그렇게 하여 얻은 것.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of a monk going around to ask for an offering, or something obtained by doing so.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>구걸 [구걸]</dt><br>
<dd>1. begging</dd><br>
<dd>남에게 돈이나 먹을 것, 물건 등을 대가 없이 달라고 함.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of asking others for money, food, stuff, etc., for free and without any cost to oneself.</dd><br>
<dd>2. plea</dd><br>
<dd>남에게 어떤 일이나 행동을 해 달라고 애원함.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of pleading with others to do a certain kind of work or take a certain kind of action.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>걸식 [걸씩]</dt><br>
<dd>begging; mendicancy</dd><br>
<dd>생활을 하기 위하여 남에게 음식을 구걸하여 거저 얻어먹음.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of begging for free food from others as a way of living.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>